    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Well spaceous play grounds that helps the sports persons to take training",
          "name": "Vishnu Priya",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "I really like the infrastructure and the way of faculties teaching to students",
          "name": "Vishnu Priya",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "And the mist thing the food in canteen is so good",
          "name": "Dinesh kumar",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "I really love the Infrastructure that they are maintaining inside the city with less place",
          "name": "Dinesh kumar",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Good lab facilities and we can use any lab even for our own educational purposes",
          "name": "Review Ranger",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Friendly staff and teaching. Faculties are ready to assist us anytime",
          "name": "Review Ranger",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Excellent placement training and opportunities",
          "name": "Review Ranger",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Hell lot of freedom for boys you can roam wherever you want between 8:00am_9:30pm beyond which you need to have decent negotiation skills to convince the warden . however saturdays are free night where you dont have any restrictions",
          "name": "Srimathi",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The sanitary facilities of the college is remarkable and the restrooms are always clean and neat.",
          "name": "Mithun Maheshvar",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Our college has good study environment as well as extracurricular. We have approximately 31 clubs",
          "name": "Tharika S",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Girls are not allowed to anywhere after 6.30 pm even inside campus.",
          "name": "Abitha shiny",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Colleges timing 8.30 to 4.45 more time college consumes",
          "name": "Abitha shiny",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "College needs to conduct proper fests like Rivera , mood indigo etc... Professors should improve on their communication skills so that it will be helpful for the non native folks",
          "name": "Srimathi",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Girls on the other hand are imposed stringent restrictions but it is much better than few colleges like Amritha, VIT in that aspect",
          "name": "Srimathi",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Other than studies and placement there's nothing much.",
          "name": "Mithun Maheshvar",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The culturals and importance to such activities are less.",
          "name": "Mithun Maheshvar",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The opportunities given for sports persons by the physical director is questionable.",
          "name": "Mithun Maheshvar",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "I felt Campus could have been much bigger",
          "name": "Tharika S",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Very long college hours and mostly no holiday will be given on Saturday",
